Sazka Stops Its Lottery Business, Hospodarske Noviny Reports

-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 
2011-05-26T06:29:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/sazka-stops-its-lottery-business-hospodarske-noviny-reports.html
Sazka AS, the Czech lottery provider
facing bankruptcy, announced to the  Finance Ministry  it has
stopped its lottery activities,  Hospodarske Noviny  reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Ales Husak.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  